/* # EduQuiz
ok

EduQuiz is a fun and interactive quiz application designed to make learning enjoyable for young explorers. Users can select from a variety of quiz categories, choose their preferred difficulty level, and embark on engaging quiz adventures with instant feedback and celebratory animations. Additionally, quiz creators can manage their own quizzes, fostering a dynamic and personalized learning environment.

